SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       mkdir(2)

       The full documentation for mmkkddiirr is maintained as a Texinfo manual.  If the iinnffoo and mmkkddiirr programs are prop‐
       erly installed at your site, the command

              iinnffoo ccoorreeuuttiillss ''mmkkddiirr iinnvvooccaattiioonn''

       should give you access to the complete manual.



